<view class="page bubble-page">
  <view class="page-head floral-title-box">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--blue"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <text class="seal-flower">泡泡站</text>
    <text class="hero-title">吗喽的泡泡机</text>
    <text class="subtext">不用立刻解决人生。先摇一颗泡泡。</text>
  </view>

  <character-card image="{{companion.image}}" name="{{companion.name}}" tag="{{companion.tag}}" message="{{companion.message}}" sub-message="{{companion.subMessage}}" variant="{{companion.variant}}" size="{{companion.size}}" />

  <view class="floral-divider"><view class="floral-divider__line"></view><view class="floral-divider__dot blue"></view><view class="floral-divider__dot"></view><view class="floral-divider__line"></view></view>
  <view class="note-card bubble-note paper-edge"><text>泡泡会轻轻提醒你：有些话可以接住，有些职场废话可以点破。</text></view>

  <view class="ornament-card ornament-card--blue bubble-machine">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--blue"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <view class="machine-window">
      <view class="machine-circle"></view>
      <view class="machine-bubble b1"></view>
      <view class="machine-bubble b2"></view>
      <view class="machine-bubble b3"></view>
      <view class="machine-base"></view>
      <text class="machine-label">MALO BUBBLE</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{bubble}}" class="ornament-card bubble-card {{bubble.tone}} {{bubble.tone === 'ld' && poppedMessage ? 'popped-card' : ''}}">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--purple"></view>
    <view class="bubble-orb" style="background: {{bubble.color}};"></view>
    <text class="seal-flower">{{bubble.source}}</text>
    <text class="chip bubble-type">{{bubble.type}}</text>
    <text class="bubble-text">{{bubble.text}}</text>
    <button wx:if="{{bubble.tone === 'ld' && !poppedMessage}}" class="sticker-button secondary" bindtap="popLdBubble">点破这句职场废话</button>
    <text wx:if="{{poppedMessage}}" class="popped">{{poppedMessage}}</text>
  </view>

  <view wx:else class="empty-card bubble-empty"><text>泡泡还没出现。按一下按钮，让它咕噜一下。</text></view>
  <button class="sticker-button" bindtap="drawBubble">摇一颗泡泡</button>
  <view class="floral-divider"><view class="floral-divider__line"></view><view class="floral-divider__dot red"></view><view class="floral-divider__dot green"></view><view class="floral-divider__line"></view></view>
</view>
